                                <img class="img-fluid d-block mx-auto" src="~/Content/img/screen3.png" alt="Nice Bowling" />
                                <p>Nice Bowling! was created to be played on both console and mobile, revolving around the simple mechanic of throwing the ball down the lange.  A huge assortment of quirky, random effects are introdcued in every frame, making each playthrough unique.  Multiple balls of differing size, weights, and physics materials can make the frame more or less challenging.  Pin size can change, wind can knock you off course, obsticals, ramps, and even piles of floppy fishes can spawn on the lane.</p>

                                <p>Nice Bowling! also carries its identity in its sleek, radical look.  We put a huge focus on neon colors, moving, glowing grids, video effects that hearken back to the wonder years of VHS tapes... And to top it all off, we've got a sick retro/vaporwave soundtrack that compliments the whole experience.</p>
